    or refining user experiences for greater impact. I thrive in collaborative environments and value strong, 
    supportive teams - but I'm equally effective when working independently.
  </p>
  <p class="sm:text-justify">
   I'm always excited to push the boundaries of technology and make a meaningful impact. 
   Let's connect - whether it's to talk tech, your favorite metal band, or potential collaborations. ü§ùüèº
  </p>
  <div class="flex justify-center mt-12">
    <img src="https://whats-lasitha-now-playing.vercel.app/now-playing" alt="Now Playing" />
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  :global(.details-photo > svg) {
    position: absolute;
    left: 20px;
    top: -10px;
    z-index: -1;
    transition: var(--transition);
  }
  .details-photo {
    transition: var(--transition);
    margin-bottom: 1em;
  }

  .details-photo:hover {
    transform: translate(3px, -3px);
  }

  .details-photo:hover img {
    transition: var(--transition);
  }

  :global(.details-photo:hover > svg) {
    transform: translate(6px, -6px);
  }

  .me {
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    position: relative;
    background-image: url("/src/assets/images/blur.png");
    background-size: contain;
  }
  h2::before {
    content: "";
    display: block;
    position: absolute;
    width: 90px;
    height: 1px;
    left: -120px;
    margin: 0px auto;
    background-color: var(--clr-quote);
    top: 50%;
  }
  h2::after {
    content: "";
    display: block;
    position: absolute;
    width: 90px;
    height: 1px;
    right: -120px;
    margin: 0px auto;
    background-color: var(--clr-quote);
    top: 50%;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .details {
      display: block;
    }

    img {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .details-photo:hover {
      transform: translate(0px, -5px);
    }
  }
</style>
